Clinic LPN | Tulsa, OK This position is full-time. Other positions and PRN positions available.   Clinic LPN Requirements:
  • 2 years clinical experience
  • Oklahoma LPN license in good standing
  Clinic LPN Duties:
  • Assist physician in the clinic back office duties
  Clinic LPN Compensation:
  • Compensation is dependent on experience
